{"tid":1659803,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港十公里挑戰賽收警方反對通知書　田總決定上訴","createTime":"2019-10-17T06:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T06:58:40.000Z","uid":246731,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"942f8df82030ae79da4e71379f0c43cc1973c877","tid":1659803,"uid":246731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"香港業餘田徑總會昨日（16日）宣布，原定於本月27日在天水圍舉行的「新鴻基地產香港十公里挑戰賽」，因接獲警方發出反對通知書，令賽事被迫取消。不過田總昨晚表示，與各持分者經再三商討後，非常希望活動能夠繼續舉辦，故已向警方提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n天水圍天影路舉行　報名名額6000個<br />\n田總昨於facebook專頁中公布，因接獲警方對比賽發出反對通知，故今年的「香港十公里挑戰賽」賽事取消。該項活動原定於本月27日舉行，賽事自2003年起於天水圍天影路舉行，今年亦以天影路為起點及終點；起跑時間為上午8時，比賽限時1.5小時，男女子組各設青年組、壯年組、先進1組及先進2組；而隊際組別則設男子隊際、女子隊際及青年混合隊，比賽名額有6,000人。<br />\n<br />\n軍政府連跑步都要限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373efde26162f25e5380c32cb4511d4c411ea304","tid":1659803,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"67cfccafe766fbf9445d86fe05e8f7fee1bb7ae1","tid":1659803,"uid":246731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:58:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/387187/逃犯條例-香港十公里挑戰賽收警方反對通知書-田總決定上訴?itm_source=universal_search&amp;itm_campaign=universal_search&amp;itm_content=十公里&amp;itm_medium=web\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F387187%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0%E8%B3%BD%E6%94%B6%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8-%E7%94%B0%E7%B8%BD%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%3Fitm_source%3Duniversal_search%26itm_campaign%3Duniversal_search%26itm_content%3D%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%26itm_medium%3Dweb&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgH